While writing other people’s emotions, she may have neglected her own. Violet Evergarden, the child soldier turned Auto Memory Doll, writes letters that evoke the words her clients can’t. But when a terminally ill boy requests her services for his family, her own feelings about love and loss resurface. Now she must confront her past and the death of the Major.
(Source: Funimation)
Sekai Saikou no Ansatsusha, Isekai Kizoku ni Tensei suru
Action, Adventure, Drama, Fantasy, Mystery, Romance

The world's number one assassin has been reincarnated as the eldest son of a family of aristocrat assassins. In exchange for being reincarnated in another world, a goddess has imposed upon him one condition. "Kill the Hero who is prophesied to destroy the world."
This was to be the mission in his new life. The synergistic effect of the vast knowledge and experience he gained that made all manner of assassinations possible in the modern world, and the secret techniques and magic of the fantasy world's most powerful family of assassins turn him into the greatest assassin of all time.
(Source: Crunchyroll)
Ushiro no Seki no Gal ni Sukarete Shimatta. Mou Ore wa Damekamoshirenai

Sandai Fujiwara, a socially bottom-tier boy, sits in front of Shino Yuizaki, a beautiful gal at the top of the social caste.
Physically, they are very close to each other, but with their difference in status, it feels like they live in different worlds, never crossing paths with each other.
Until Sandai found Shino stuck in a ditch, having accidentally slipped.
“Thanks for the shower”
“Well, goodbye then.”
Although he takes Shino home on a whim to let her shower, Sandai remains wary of the gal. However, he finds himself increasingly attracted to Shino, who despite her looks, is actually not that experienced with men, even as she aggressively approaches him.
After some trouble, the two start dating, and begin to spend their days sweetly flirting with each other…….
Tobioriru Chokuzen no Doukyuusei ni "XXX Shiyou!" to Teian Shitemita.

My first love, her name is Koga Gumomo.

She was so much more beautiful and mature than a typical high school student, which attracted a great deal of jealousy and dislike. So much so that she was on the verge of jumping off the rooftop because of all the bullying she received.

So, what can I do to help?

"Why not have s*x with me!"
"............, you pervert! ...... (yuck!)"
"Maybe so! But are you sure? If you die here, your last memory will be the confession of some pervert you don't even know! It would ruin the mood!"
"............, what have you done! You pervert!"
"I have my reasons. Because I love you more than anything in the world! Let's get married!"
"What, ehhhh~~~............?"

I will yell out my love until I die, if it will make a place for you in this world!

The most stupid and straightforward protagonist in the history of romantic comedies and the cool, sullen JK will hook up for a romantic comedy with a sugar content of 100%!

(Source: Dengeki Bunko, translated)
